name: Hustcc's Github Sitemap
body:
### 1. iReact
Fantastic React Components and Libraries! Makes it easy for you to pick one that’ll work for you.

Github: [https://github.com/hustcc/iReact](https://github.com/hustcc/iReact)

Website: [http://ireact.cn/](http://ireact.cn/)


### 2. echarts-for-react
baidu Echarts(v3.0) components for React wrapper. 一个简单的echarts(v3.0)的react封装。

Github: [https://github.com/hustcc/echarts-for-react](https://github.com/hustcc/echarts-for-react)

Website: [http://git.hust.cc/echarts-for-react](http://git.hust.cc/echarts-for-react)


### 3. placeholder.js
< 1Kb library to generate image placeholders on client side.

Github: [https://github.com/hustcc/placeholder.js](https://github.com/hustcc/placeholder.js)

Website: [http://placeholder.cn/](http://placeholder.cn/)


### 4. canvas-nest.js
Interactive Particle / Nest System With JavaScript and Canvas, Do not Depends on jQuery.

Github: [https://github.com/hustcc/canvas-nest.js/](https://github.com/hustcc/canvas-nest.js/)

Website: [http://git.hust.cc/canvas-nest.js/](http://git.hust.cc/canvas-nest.js/), [http://www.atool.org/](http://www.atool.org/)


### 5. horse.js
< 3Kb. autocomplete component of pure javascript. 纯Javascript实现的轻量简洁的提示组件。includes every sane browser and IE7+.

Github: [https://github.com/hustcc/horse.js](https://github.com/hustcc/horse.js)

Website: [http://git.hust.cc/horse.js/](http://git.hust.cc/horse.js/)


### Support or Contact
About me, to [https://github.com/hustcc](https://github.com/hustcc).
